        ''' <summary>
        ''' Adds a set of Resources to the grid (i.e., resources that were added since calling Populate).
        ''' </summary>
        ''' <param name="Resources">The Resources to add.  They must already be present in the ResourceFile.</param>
        ''' <remarks></remarks>
